<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="objectType">stele</rs> (Grabplatte) with a gable drawn above, and a relief below ( <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.41</measure> x  <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.21</measure> x  <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.07</measure>). There is a <rs type="decoration">rosette</rs> in the gable. The relief is of a  
<rs type="decoration">shepherd</rs>, with a <rs type="decoration">cloak</rs> on his shoulders and a <rs type="decoration">staff</rs>; beside him are ?a <rs type="decoration">sheep</rs> and a <rs type="decoration">dog</rs>.</p>
</div>
